'''''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'' 6''' is the sixth issue of [[Star Wars Insider|''The Lucasfilm Fan Club Magazine'']], later rebranded as the ''Star Wars Insider''. Issue 6 was published in Winter [[1989]].

{{Magazine-stub|issue}}

==Contents==
===Departments===
*"The Fan Forum"
*"[[Collections]]: If Collecting Has A Name, It Must Be Indiana Jones" by [[Adam Schultz]]
*"[[Inside ILM]]" by [[John S. Davis]]

===Features===
*"[[George Lucas: The Force Behind Lucasfilm]]" by [[Dan Madsen]]
*"John Pomeroy: Producing ''The Land Before Time''" by [[Lisa E. Cowan|Lisa Cowan]]
*"A Design of Destiny: The Making of a Dream" by Lisa E. Cowan
*"Sneak Preview: ''Indiana Jones and the Last Crusade''"
*"Kevin Pollak: Playing Small, But Thinking Big" by Dan Madsen

